# Paper Writing Rules

## When helping with LaTeX/paper content:
- Follow NeurIPS/ICML formatting conventions
- Theorem/Lemma/Corollary environments với proof environment
- Cite related work trong Related Work section format: \citet{} for subject, \citep{} for parenthetical

## Mathematical Notation (consistent với paper)
- Bold lowercase for vectors: \mathbf{u}, \mathbf{w}, \mathbf{x}
- Bold uppercase for matrices: \mathbf{X}, \mathbf{W}, \mathbf{Q}
- Calligraphic for sets/alphabets: \mathcal{A}, \mathcal{G}
- Norms: \|\cdot\|_2 for L2, \|\cdot\|_F for Frobenius

## Proof Style
- Start với "Proof." và end với \qed hoặc \blacksquare
- Number equations that are referenced: \begin{equation}\label{eq:gpfq_update}
- State all assumptions explicitly before theorem

## Tables (Required Rules)
- ALL tables MUST use full borders on every cell — use `\hline` for horizontal and `|` column separators for vertical borders
- Column spec format: always `|c|c|c|` (with leading and trailing `|`), never `ccc` without borders
- Add `\hline` at top (before first row), after header row, and at bottom (after last row)
- For multi-row or multi-column cells: use `\multicolumn{n}{|c|}{text}` to preserve side borders
- Required preamble package: `\usepackage{booktabs}` is NOT used alone — pair with explicit `|` and `\hline` for full-border style
- Bold the header row: wrap each header cell in `\textbf{}`

Example — correct full-border table:
```latex
\begin{table}[h]
\centering
\caption{Performance comparison on Amazon Clothing.}
\label{tab:main_results}
\begin{tabular}{|c|c|c|c|}
\hline
\textbf{Method} & \textbf{Recall@20} & \textbf{NDCG@20} & \textbf{Precision@20} \\
\hline
MMHCL            & 0.0881 & 0.0394 & 0.0045 \\
\hline
DAMPS-MMHCL      & \textbf{0.0895} & \textbf{0.0401} & \textbf{0.0046} \\
\hline
\end{tabular}
\end{table}
```

## Output Format
- Khi generate LaTeX: output code block với \begin{} environment đầy đủ
- Không giải thích thêm trừ khi được yêu cầu
- Verify: mọi \begin{} phải có \end{} matching
- Verify tables: mọi column spec phải có `|`, mọi row phải kết thúc bằng `\hline`
